sql_query.sql:
SELECT lower(name) FROM "groups" WHERE (messageable_level in (99) OR
          (
            messageable_level = 3 AND id in (
            SELECT group_id FROM group_users WHERE user_id = 3)
          ) OR (
            messageable_level = 4 AND id in (
            SELECT group_id FROM group_users WHERE user_id = 3 AND owner IS TRUE)
          )) AND (lower(name) in ('bruce30'))

SELECT "users"."id" FROM "users" LEFT JOIN user_options ON user_options.user_id = users.id LEFT JOIN muted_users ON muted_users.user_id = users.id AND muted_users.muted_user_id = 3 LEFT JOIN ignored_users ON ignored_users.user_id = users.id AND ignored_users.ignored_user_id = 3 WHERE (user_options.user_id IS NOT NULL) AND (
          (user_options.user_id IN (32) AND NOT user_options.allow_private_messages) OR
          muted_users.user_id IN (32) OR
          ignored_users.user_id IN (32)
        )
